Uses of Package
pollaxmud.entities

  • Packages that use pollaxmud.entities 
    Package Description
    pollaxmud.entities
    A package that contains all the game entities, such as creatures and items.
    pollaxmud.gui
    Package used to store GUI stuff.
    pollaxmud.handlers
    A package with different kind of handlers which handles different kind of stuff in the game.
    pollaxmud.utilities
    A package full of useful utilities for the game.
    pollaxmud.world
    A package that contains all classes belonging to the game world.
  • Classes in pollaxmud.entities used by pollaxmud.entities 
    Class and Description
    Book
    This class represents a Book, which inherits from the Item class.
    Course
    This class represents a course.
    Creature
    The creature class.
    Item
    This class is used to represent Items, which other classes representing more specific items inherits from.
    Player
    Class for representing the Player that the person that is playing the game is controlling.
    Question
    A question to be asked by teachers.
